WEBVTT

00:15:31.868 --> 00:15:35.328
So you're learning everything you can
about your line of work,

00:15:35.352 --> 00:15:37.256
ready to help wherever you can.

00:15:37.280 --> 00:15:40.710
But be aware that sometimes
no good deed goes unpunished.

00:15:41.133 --> 00:15:44.117
There are certain ways that
becoming a big helper can backfire,

00:15:44.141 --> 00:15:45.694
especially for women.

00:15:46.831 --> 00:15:48.419
New research by economists shows

00:15:48.443 --> 00:15:51.395
that women get 44 percent
more requests than men

00:15:51.419 --> 00:15:53.513
to volunteer for thankless tasks.

00:15:53.537 --> 00:15:55.363
You know, the office housework:

00:15:55.387 --> 00:15:57.934
taking notes in meetings, planning events.

00:15:57.958 --> 00:16:00.569
Women also feel more pressure to say yes,